        	* gcc/dwarf2.h (DW_AT_SUN_amd64_parmdump): New.
        	* gcc/dwarf2out.c (gen_subprogram_die): Add this attribute.
        	* gcc/doc/invoke.texi (-msave-args): New x86-64 option.
